#ExpandedExplanation
#Palette FF Stays the same - Last 3 are tile codes
#if first digit is 1 that means left/right and up/down
#if all digits are 0 that means left/right
#if second digit is 1 that means up/down
#if first and second are 1 that means left 1 and down 2 ????
#if third digit is 1 that means right (reserverd singular sprites)
#,0,-8   up          010
#,0,8    down        010
#,-8,0   left        000
#,-8,-8  left/up     100
#,-8,8   left/down   100
#,8,0    right       000
#,8,-8   right/up    100
#,8,8    right/down  100


#ExpandedSpritesLeft (Needs a lot of work for each frame)

#ExpandedExplanation
#Palette FF Stays the same - Last 3 are tile codes
#if first digit is 1 that means left/right and up/down
#if all digits are 0 that means left/right
#if second digit is 1 that means up/down
#if first and second are 1 that means left 1 and down 2 ????
#if third digit is 1 that means right (reserverd singular sprites)
#,0,-8   up          010
#,0,8    down        010
#,-8,0   left        000
#,-8,-8  left/up     100
#,-8,8   left/down   100
#,8,0    right       000
#,8,-8   right/up    100
#,8,8    right/down  100
